data.title: What movie and television projects has Iain Lauchlan been in?
data.meta_description:
Iain Armstrong has: Played Technician in "Doctor Who" in 1963.
Played Robert in "BBC2 Playhouse" in 1974. Played Second in "The
Swordsman" in 1974. Played First Gentleman in "King Lear" in 1982.
Played Villager in "Robin of Sherwood" in 1984. Played Mr. Hewlett
in "The Killing Zone" in 1999.
data.text:
Iain Connell has: Played Gordon Conway in "Rab C. Nesbitt" in 1988. Played Wendall in "Legit" in 2007. Played Husband in "Empty" in 2008. Played Various in "Burnistoun" in 2009. Performed in "Burnistoun" in 2009.

Callum Cuthbertson has: Played Gleason in "Rab C. Nesbitt" in 1988. Played Employment Clerk in "Rab C. Nesbitt" in 1988. Played Drew in "Ruffian Hearts" in 1995. Played Radio Operator in "Breaking the Waves" in 1996. Played Man in "How High the Castle Walls" in 1997. Played Norman in "Rockface" in 2002. Played Blowhard in "Still Game" in 2002. Played Norman - Hotel Manager in "Rockface" in 2002. Played Weighmaster in "Dear Green Place" in 2006. Played Peter in "How Not to Live Your Life" in 2007. Played Archie Boddington in "Empty" in 2008. Played Martin McLintoch in "Gary Tank Commander" in 2009. Played Martin in "Gary Tank Commander" in 2009. Performed in "Not Another Happy Ending" in 2013.
